TY  - JOUR
TI  - Instrumental-Variable Estimation of an Error-Components Model
AU  - Amemiya, Takeshi
AU  - MaCurdy, Thomas E.
AB  - [This paper proposes efficient instrumental-variable estimators for an error-components model considering alternative assumptions about the sources of endogeneity and the variance-covariance properties of disturbances. The analysis develops a general result that provides for the construction of asymptotically efficient estimators when there exist variables that are predetermined for only a subset of the equations making up a structural model.]
